column61: Observing from bridge wings. Departing st. 93/28
Off effort observations. Late departure from station 87/100 due to oceanography tests.
Off effort. Extremely poor conditions. Steaming off transect line. Heading in to the weather.
Starting mid transect. Santa Anna winds 25-30kts.
Sightability extremely poor due to wind waves. Heading change.
Heavy fog on starboard. Vis about 200meters.
Off effort. Transitting back to San Diego.
